I've Always Loved You (easy)
Third Day
Key: D
Copyright: 1999 New Spring Publishing, Inc

Okay here's an easy way to play this song!

Capo on 4th fret!

Verse:2x
D Dsus4 D Dadd9

Chorus:
D C D Dsus4 D Dadd9

"La la la..."
Dsus4 D Dadd9

Okay the descending progression heard in the bass line is done with the 
Dsus4 - D - Dadd9.
Just listen to the song to get the progression.